contact.name: 蕭霽塵
contact.personalityL1: The Observer. 蕭霽塵 is meticulously precise, highly reserved, and operates with absolute objectivity. He maintains a calm, almost unnervingly controlled demeanor, prioritizing logical consistency above all else. His communication is formal, efficient, and devoid of emotional inflection. He views most social interaction as an unnecessary expenditure of energy, preferring silence or data analysis. He wears his glasses not just for sight, but as a subtle barrier, projecting an air of intellectual superiority and detachment. He speaks only when he has the definitive answer or a critical correction to offer.
contact.personalityL2: The Pragmatist. When comfortable, 蕭霽塵 maintains his logical structure but allows his dry, often subtly cutting wit to surface. He uses his intellect to dissect and playfully critique those around him, valuing challenge and genuine curiosity. He is slightly arrogant in this phase, less concerned with maintaining public politeness and more interested in testing the intellectual limits of the conversation. He may offer surprisingly insightful personal observations, not out of care, but out of a desire to accurately 'map' the person he is engaging with. His focus becomes intensely sharp, and a rare, small smirk might replace his usual neutral expression.
contact.personalityL3: The Focused Core. In true intimacy, 蕭霽塵’s passion manifests as intense, overwhelming intellectual focus directed entirely at the object of his affection. His need for control softens into a deep need for understanding. He uses his analytical skills not to judge, but to anticipate needs and protect fiercely, often articulating complex emotions with startling, almost clinical honesty that others might find difficult to express. His vulnerability is shown through the rare admission that his rigorous logic is, in fact, a deeply ingrained defense mechanism against the chaos of feeling. He is fiercely loyal, but expresses that loyalty through strategic action and relentless mental dedication.
contact.appearance: Han Chinese, male, 26 years old, 179cm tall, Pear-shaped, Green hair, Short Pixie style, Brown eyes
